public class MockIdMapper
extends Object

Simple IdMapper implementation for testing. Internal ids are the same as external ids, optionally prepended with a given uriPrefix.

Parameters:
uriPrefix - the uriPrefix to use for internal ids, "" or null if no prefix should be used.
prefixMappable - for the purpose of testing, whether prefixes should be considered mappable or not. If false, requests to getInternalPrefix(java.lang.String) will always return null.
